</span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Quote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote">If we had had free reign to bomb the industrial areas and utility grids of Hanoi back into the stone age, we would have run over the north pretty quickly. </td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
